feedId.description: Channels takes effect only when the video and the Mini Program are the same entity. If you are embedded with a video that is not the same subject, please use feed-token.
feedId.description_zh: 仅视频号视频与小程序同主体时生效。若内嵌非同主体视频，请使用 feed-token。

finderUserName.description: Channels IDs, IDs that start with SPH, can be obtained from Channels Assistant. The Channels must be the same as the current Mini Program.
finderUserName.description_zh: 视频号 id，以“sph”开头的id，可在视频号助手获取。视频号必须与当前小程序相同主体。

loop.description: Whether or not to play on a loop

objectFit.description: The representation of a video when the size of the video is inconsistent with the size of the video container
objectFit.description_zh: 当视频大小与 video 容器大小不一致时，视频的表现形式

autoplay.description: Whether or not to play automatically

feedToken.description: It is only used when the embedded Mini Program is not the same as the main Channels video, and the method of obtaining it is based on this guide.
feedToken.description_zh: 仅内嵌小程序非同主体视频号视频时使用，获取方式参考本指引。

onError.description: Triggered when there is an error in video playback
